                     <interp inst="t18320906-379-person3114" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Police-constable. About two o'clock in the morning I was with Pye, and heard the alarm; I received the prisoner - he said he had picked the shawl up in the road; I asked if nobody claimed it - he said Yes, there was a man claimed it; I took him back, and met the prosecutor.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I picked it up in the road.</p>
